@hakatagensukesydney NOW OPEN @regentplace_sydney 
From Hakata to Melbourne in 2014, the very best Tonkotsu Ramen now open it’s 9th store in the heart of Sydney CBD. It will feature it’s classic menu; Signature Tonkotsu, Black Tonkotsu, God Fire, Shio Tonkotsu, Chicken Karaage and Hitokuchi Gyoza. 🍜

🎉🌸 Get ready for the EPIC LAUNCH NEXT THURSDAY FROM 5:00PM of a flavor spectacle! Introducing the Sakura Mont Blanc and Matcha Mont Blanc! 🍵🌸 Brace yourselves for an explosion of taste and elegance starting at 5pm on August 17th! 🚀🕔 Be the FIRST 100 in line to receive $10 vouchers as we kick off this culinary extravaganza! 🎁🙌 Don’t miss out, it’s a LIMITED EDITION sensation that’s here until stocks last! 🍰🎈 Join us in making history with these two exclusive delights! 🌟👑

🇭🇰 Discover the Essence of Hong Kong 🥢🍞 @8.52newtown 

Welcome to 8:52 Hong Kong Restaurant, Newtown’s first-ever taste of authentic Hong Kong classics! Indulge in our signature Hong Kong-style French toast and savor the cultural flavors now in Newtown. 🏮🍽️ 
#852HongKongRestaurant

@slimsqualityburger at @westfieldsyd 
ON THE MENU: 
🍔 🇺🇸 The Nashville-inspired Blazin’ Hot Chicken Burger: a succulent, hand-crumb coated, flash-fried chicken breast with a signature cayenne spice blend, pepper jack cheese, spicy mayo, coleslaw, and gambino NY Bronx pickles on a freshly toasted potato bun 🍔 🇺🇸 

🔥 🍟 The fiery Inferno Fries: fresh-cut chips topped with Himalayan pink salt, shredded cheddar cheese, spicy mayo, pickles, and a spray of pickle brine to ensure the spice blend sticks to every frie 🔥 🍟 

🥤🥤A refreshing Cherry Limeade: fresh-squeezed lime juice, cherry syrup, and soda with tubelet-micro ice. 🥤🥤
